overview:
Restaurant, Osteria, Pizzeria or Trattoria, ACTIVATE YOUR PERSONAL WEBSITE! Meet a new active service on the web where you will have the opportunity to learn about your business to thousands of web surfers! Search Your Restaurant  www.OsteriaoRistorante.it

Enabling your site, you will be able to: • Make your company known to thousands of people • Present in the best way your company through photos chosen by you • enticed customers on the site showing your exceptional menu • Being contacted by prospective customers by mail or telephone • To be found immediately with the interactive Google map • Organizing events and let everyone know about what will take place and most importantly, what will taste! Think of events such as New Year, Christmas, Valentine’s Day, Women’s Day, Fairs, Local Festivals Football Matches! • To delight the palate more of your customers to know you can do some of your recipes! • And finally, thanks to the management of the reviews, you will know the value of your company through the advice of your own customers! Also, when your company will be reviewed in by users, will be automatically entered in the culinary experiences of users interested in its style (BETA) Important, enabling your site, you will be on the search portal “OsterieORistoranti.it” with greater visibility: • Can be searched using the filter “Restaurants with Showcase” • Increased evidence of companies with active site (colors, links, votes) • Presence of average scores on the portal for your company • Presence on search engines (Google, Bing, Yahoo, etc.), so visible to the world

All this for FREE!
